    <h1>SignalService</h1>

    <p>SignalService is a modular .NET 10 microservice that provides:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Web API endpoints</li>
        <li>gRPC service</li>
        <li>SignalR hubs</li>
        <li>Background job processing</li>
        <li>Azure Service Bus integration</li>
        <li>Functional test clients (Web API, gRPC, SignalR, Service Bus)</li>
    </ul>

    <p>The project is fully containerized and includes Kubernetes deployment manifests.</p>

    <hr />

